'''2021年世界高山滑雪锦标赛'''是第46届[[世界高山滑雪锦标赛|世界高山滑雪锦标赛]]，于2021年2月8日至21日在意大利科尔蒂纳丹佩佐举行。科尔蒂纳丹佩佐于2016年6月10日确认获得该届比赛主办权<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.srf.ch/sport/ski-alpin/ski-alpin-allgemein/ski-wm-2021-in-cortina-d-ampezzo|script-title=de:Ski-WM 2021 in Cortina d'Ampezzo|publisher={{lang|de|Schweizer Radio und Fernsehen}}|date=2016-06-10|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813095820/https://www.srf.ch/sport/ski-alpin/ski-alpin-allgemein/ski-wm-2021-in-cortina-d-ampezzo|archivedate=2018-08-13}}</ref>。因应[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]，意大利冬季运动联合会一度于2020年5月向[[国际滑雪联合会|国际滑雪联合会]]申请将该届比赛推迟至2022年<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1094637/2021-fis-alpine-world-chamionships |title= Cortina 2021 organisers request FIS Alpine World Ski Championships move to 2022 |work=Inside the Games|first= Ali |last= Iveson |date=2020-05-25 |accessdate=2021-03-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802150811/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1094637/2021-fis-alpine-world-chamionships |archivedate=2020-08-02 }}</ref>，但被国际滑雪联合会拒绝<ref>{{cite news|url=https://skiracing.com/fis-alpine-world-ski-championships-2021-in-cortina-confirmed/ |title=FIS Alpine World Ski Championships 2021 in Cortina confirmed |work=Ski Racing |date=2020-07-02 |accessdate=2021-02-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206213153/https://skiracing.com/fis-alpine-world-ski-championships-2021-in-cortina-confirmed/ |archivedate=2021-02-06 }}</ref>。最终比赛按照原定计划开赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cortina2021.com/en/fis-alpine-world-ski-championships-start-with-double-super-g/|title=FIS Alpine World Ski Championships start with double Super-G women at 10.45, men at 13.00|work=Cortina 2021|date=2021-02-10|accessdate=2021-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214122828/https://www.cortina2021.com/en/fis-alpine-world-ski-championships-start-with-double-super-g/|archivedate=2021-02-14}}</ref>。

